OL,3,C'It's 13 years and we still can't see
OL,4,Cthe finishing line'
OL,6,FHomeowners are still waiting for
OL,7,Fbotched insulation to be removed more
OL,8,Fthan two years after funding was
OL,9,Fgranted to complete the work.
OL,11,FMore than a hundred houses in Bridgend
OL,12,Fcounty were damaged by insulation
OL,13,Finstalled as part of an energy
OL,14,Fefficiency drive over a decade ago.
OL,16,FResidents in Caerau near Maesteg say
OL,17,Fthey've endured damp, mouldy and cold
OL,18,Fconditions ever since.
