OL,3,C'It's 13 years and we still can't see
OL,4,Cthe finishing line'
OL,6,FBridgend council says it's now
OL,7,Fpreparing the work on all 104
OL,8,Fproperties affected, even though only
OL,9,F25 of them had the insulation
OL,10,Finstalled by the council.
OL,12,F12 years ago Geraint Goodgridge's
OL,13,Fgrandmother had insulation installed
OL,14,Fin their house.
OL,16,FIt was supposed to reduce her heating
OL,17,Fbill, but he says rather than making
OL,18,Flives easier it's ruined them.
