OL,3,C'It's 13 years and we still can't see
OL,4,Cthe finishing line'
OL,6,F"I've had to knock the porch down, re-
OL,7,Fdo it all and there's still damp
OL,8,Fcoming though", said Geraint.
OL,10,F"It's just a waste of money really.
OL,11,FIt's not ok for an 86 year-old woman."
OL,13,FGeraint's granmother passed away a
OL,14,Fyear ago. He doesn't want to move in
OL,15,Funtil the damp is fixed - and there's
OL,16,Fstill no date for when that might
OL,17,Fhappen.
OL,19,FGeraint explained: "It's crazy, I'm
OL,20,Fworking just to get work done on the
OL,21,Fhouse that the council have caused."
