OL,3,C'It's 13 years and we still can't see
OL,4,Cthe finishing line'
OL,6,FIn 2022, the Welsh Government
OL,7,Fcommitted more than #2.6 million to
OL,8,Fmake repairs to homes in the area,
OL,9,Fwhile Bridgend council said they would
OL,10,Fcontribute #800,000.
OL,12,FBut residents are concerned works may
OL,13,Fstill not begin until next year.
OL,15,FRitchie Humphreys has lived just down
OL,16,Fthe road from Geraint for 60 years. He
OL,17,Fsays dealing with the effects of the
OL,18,Fbotched insulation is getting more
OL,19,Fdifficult.
