OL,3,C'It's 13 years and we still can't see
OL,4,Cthe finishing line'
OL,6,F"We thought our life would be tidy now
OL,7,Fbut it's just stress. It's 13 years
OL,8,Fand we still can't see the finishing
OL,9,Fline with it", he said.
OL,11,F"Trying to preserve the house by
OL,12,Fredecorating it yearly is costing a
OL,13,Flot of money and it's getting to a
OL,14,Fstage now where we can't do it - we're
OL,15,Fnot physically able to do it."
