OL,6,FBridgend Council says it has completed
OL,7,Fall retrofit assessments at each
OL,8,Feligible property since Welsh
OL,9,FGovernment funding was secured in
OL,10,FMarch 2023 for the Caerau Wall
OL,11,FInsulation Scheme.
OL,13,FIn March 2024, it appointed contractor
OL,14,FWarmworks to deliver repair works
OL,15,Facross all of the 104 eligible
OL,16,Fproperties.
