OL,4,Cthe finishing line'
OL,6,FA council statement said: "Pre-
OL,7,Fconstruction work is now underway and
OL,8,FWarmworks are liaising directly with
OL,9,Feach householder to make necessary
OL,10,Farrangements so that the works can be
OL,11,Fcarried out as efficiently as possible
OL,12,Fand with a minimum of disruption.
OL,14,F"This includes actions such as
OL,15,Forganising the temporary removal of
OL,16,Fgarden furniture and other items to
OL,17,Faccommodate scaffolding, or working
OL,18,Falongside National Grid Electricity
OL,19,FDistribution to safely remove and
OL,20,Freattach power supplies on each house.
