OL,3,C'It's 13 years and we still can't see
OL,4,Cthe finishing line'
OL,6,F"The repair works will remove existing
OL,7,Finternal and external wall insulation,
OL,8,Fand install all-new, high-quality
OL,9,Finsulation that will ensure residents
OL,10,Fcan benefit from the energy efficiency
OL,11,Fthat was promised by the original
OL,12,Fschemes.
OL,14,F"As this is not a one-size-fits-all
OL,15,Fproject, the scale of work required at
OL,16,Feach property has to meet different
OL,17,Fspecific needs.
