OL,3,C'It's 13 years and we still can't see
OL,4,Cthe finishing line'
OL,6,F"While this involves a significant
OL,7,Famount of detailed planning and
OL,8,Fpreparation, residents are being kept
OL,9,Fregularly informed about progress, and
OL,10,Fevery effort is being made to ensure
OL,11,Fthe works can be completed as quickly
OL,12,Fand as thoroughly as possible."
OL,14,FA Welsh Government spokesperson said:
OL,15,F"We have awarded #2.65million of grant
OL,16,Ffunding to Bridgend County Borough
OL,17,FCouncil to undertake remedial works on
OL,18,Faffected homes. A fully accredited
OL,19,Fcontractor has been appointed and
OL,20,Fmobilisation works are underway."
